ocols or imaged anatomical regions.\nConclusion: DNNs are recommended for accurate and robust IVIM model fitting to\nDW-MRI data. Suitable software is available at (1).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Feb 2019 22:42:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 May 2019 08:17:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
