pect to the\nconventional strategy when a covariance-aided approach is adopted.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Mar 2019 12:37:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Feb 2020 18:00:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-21"}
