aphene or carbon-based device fabrication as well\nas sensor and transistor applications, where regions of varying carrier\nconcentrations and different electrical, optical or physical properties are\ndesired.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Mar 2019 04:41:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-13"}
